OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after Trump
OL,4,Cattack on UK's response to Iran war
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer will hold talks with
OL,7,Fhis Cabinet after Donald Trump again
OL,8,Flashed out at the UK as European
OL,9,Fcountries resisted immediately
OL,10,Fagreeing to US calls for assistance in
OL,11,Freopening the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FThe Middle East crisis, and the
OL,14,Fdomestic impact of soaring oil prices
OL,15,Ftriggered by the conflict, is likely
OL,16,Fto top the agenda as the Prime
OL,17,FMinister chairs a weekly meeting with
OL,18,Fhis senior ministers on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
