PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after Trump
OL,4,Cattack on UK's response to Iran war
OL,6,FIt comes after the US President said
OL,7,Fhe was "not happy" with Britain as
OL,8,Fallies including the UK mulled how to
OL,9,Frespond to Iran's blockade of the
OL,10,Fstrait, which is a key global shipping
OL,11,Froute for oil and gas.
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer has insisted the UK
OL,14,Fwill not be drawn into a "wider war,"
OL,15,Fand said he was working with partners
OL,16,Fincluding in Europe on a "viable
OL,17,Fcollective plan" to free up navigation
OL,18,Fin the strategic sea passage.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@RO]vD@ZOUvD@eO]xD@ZOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after Trump
OL,4,Cattack on UK's response to Iran war
OL,6,FBritain could potentially provide mine-
OL,7,Fhunting drones to the mission rather
OL,8,Fthan a warship, although the Prime
OL,9,FMinister insisted no final decisions
OL,10,Fhad been made.
OL,12,F"It is a discussion, we are not at a
OL,13,Fpoint of decisions yet, I want to
OL,14,Freally stress that," he said on Monday.
OL,16,FSpeaking at a press conference later,
OL,17,FMr Trump said the US had considered
OL,18,Fthe UK the "Rolls-Royce of allies" but
OL,19,Fthat its response to the war had been
OL,20,F"very disappointing."
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@TO]zD@LOUzD@bO]|D@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
