PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after Trump
OL,4,Cattack on UK's response to Iran war
OL,6,FHe appeared to criticise Sir Keir for
OL,7,Fseeking the advice of aides on the
OL,8,Fissue of Hormuz following a call
OL,9,Fbetween the two leaders on Sunday,
OL,10,Fclaiming the Prime Minister had said
OL,11,Fhe was "meeting with my team" before
OL,12,Fmaking a decision.
OL,14,F"I said you don't need to meet with
OL,15,Fyour team, you're the Prime Minister,
OL,16,Fyou can make your own... why do you
OL,17,Fhave to meet with your team to find
OL,18,Fout whether or not you're going to
OL,19,Fsend some minesweepers to help us or
OL,20,Fto send some boats," Mr Trump said.
OL,26,@sD@HOUsD@]O]vD@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
