PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after Trump
OL,4,Cattack on UK's response to Iran war
OL,6,FUK Government sources said the Prime
OL,7,FMinister had referred to wanting to
OL,8,Fspeak to partners and military
OL,9,Fplanners, rather than No 10 advisers.
OL,11,FEuropean countries, including Germany,
OL,12,Fhave expressed a desire for more
OL,13,Fclarity over the military aims of the
OL,14,Fconflict. Many are also keen to know
OL,15,Fwhen the war will end.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
