PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after Trump
OL,4,Cattack on UK's response to Iran war
OL,6,FMr Trump has asked partners `
OL,7,Fincluding France, China, Japan, South
OL,8,FKorea and Britain ` to help secure the
OL,9,Fstrait, and claimed the US was talking
OL,10,Fto "about seven" countries but would
OL,11,Fnot say which ones.
OL,13,FHe also gave no indication of when
OL,14,Fsuch a coalition might be formed.
OL,16,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch said allies
OL,17,Fappeared "worried about how slow" the
OL,18,FPrime Minister is.
OL,26,@rD@DOUrD@PO]yD@JOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
