PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773716599
OL,3,CStarmer to chair Cabinet after Trump
OL,4,Cattack on UK's response to Iran war
OL,6,FShe told the Press Association: "I'm
OL,7,Fworried that he's not deep enough in
OL,8,Fconversations with the US. But before
OL,9,Fwe start sending ships out, we need to
OL,10,Fknow what the plan is."
OL,26,@nD@aOUrD@WO]
